   - [ ] Benchmark different configurations
   - [ ] Select optimal configuration

2. **Day 4-5: ONNX Export**
   - [ ] Export model to ONNX format
   - [ ] Verify ONNX model correctness
   - [ ] Test on ONNX Runtime
   - [ ] Compare inference speed vs PyTorch
   - [ ] Optimize ONNX graph

3. **Day 6-7: Production Preparation**
   - [ ] Package model files
   - [ ] Create model versioning system
   - [ ] Write model loading utilities
   - [ ] Document model API
   - [ ] Create model update mechanism

**Deliverables:**
- ‚úÖ Optimized ONNX model
- ‚úÖ Model package (< 200MB)
- ‚úÖ Performance benchmarks
- ‚úÖ Production integration guide

**Success Metrics:**
- Model size: < 200MB (optimized)
- Inference speed: < 1s (20-password vault)
- Accuracy maintained after optimization
- ONNX model verified on multiple platforms

