## Resource Requirements

### Team
- 1 ML Engineer (model training, optimization)
- 1 Security Engineer (crypto, security audit)
- 1 Backend Developer (API, database)
- 1 Frontend Developer (UI, UX)
- 1 DevOps Engineer (infrastructure, monitoring)
- 1 Product Manager (coordination, testing)

### Infrastructure
- GPU server for training (8+ hours)
- Production servers (AWS/GCP/Azure)
- Database cluster (PostgreSQL)
- Caching layer (Redis)
- CDN for assets

### Budget Estimate
- Development: $150,000 - $200,000 (6 months)
- Infrastructure: $5,000 - $10,000/month
- Security audit: $20,000 - $30,000
- **Total (first year)**: $230,000 - $330,000

